    "description": "Neuland Laboratories Holdings Services has an exciting opening for a Surgeon at our Vadodara office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Neuland Laboratories Holdings Services:\nNeuland Laboratories Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Neuland Laboratories Holdings Services!",
